386
00:30:04,460 --> 00:30:06,210
The servants are searching.

387
00:30:06,210 --> 00:30:07,670
We should hear something soon.

388
00:30:11,430 --> 00:30:12,160
Prik.

389
00:30:13,060 --> 00:30:14,530
Stop crying.

390
00:30:15,480 --> 00:30:17,240
Noi will be fine.

391
00:30:18,710 --> 00:30:19,750
Yes.

392
00:30:20,980 --> 00:30:21,520
Duang.

393
00:30:21,870 --> 00:30:22,340
Yes, sir.

394
00:30:22,610 --> 00:30:23,890
Report this to the police.

395
00:30:24,300 --> 00:30:24,800
Yes, sir.

396
00:30:26,800 --> 00:30:27,640
My lord.

397
00:30:29,230 --> 00:30:30,240
What is it, Waen?

398
00:30:30,920 --> 00:30:32,150
I’m certain

399
00:30:32,690 --> 00:30:34,040
this wasn’t an accident.

400
00:30:35,670 --> 00:30:36,570
But...

401
00:30:36,870 --> 00:30:38,530
someone intentionally

402
00:30:38,530 --> 00:30:39,760
sank my lady’s boat.

403
00:30:40,860 --> 00:30:42,220
Which bastard

404
00:30:42,220 --> 00:30:43,870
dared to sink my boat?

405
00:31:00,170 --> 00:31:00,720
My lord.

406
00:31:00,890 --> 00:31:02,430
Why are you panicking?

407
00:31:03,070 --> 00:31:03,740
My lord.

408
00:31:04,500 --> 00:31:06,120
Aren’t you scared?

409
00:31:08,090 --> 00:31:09,890
Shut your mouth, Yam.

410
00:31:10,410 --> 00:31:11,690
Why should I be scared?

411
00:31:12,300 --> 00:31:14,490
You sank Aunt Jumpa’s boat.

412
00:31:14,490 --> 00:31:15,370
Not me.

413
00:31:15,990 --> 00:31:16,910
I didn’t do it.

414
00:31:17,670 --> 00:31:18,400
I’m innocent.

415
00:31:21,190 --> 00:31:21,770
Gaew.

416
00:31:29,860 --> 00:31:31,520
What are you two doing here?

417
00:31:35,030 --> 00:31:35,610
Uh…

418
00:31:36,730 --> 00:31:37,690
I’m going to look for

419
00:31:37,690 --> 00:31:39,450
the one who sank Aunt Jumpa’s boat.

420
00:31:40,110 --> 00:31:41,290
I haven’t said that

421
00:31:41,990 --> 00:31:43,250
my mother’s boat sank.

422
00:31:44,310 --> 00:31:45,500
How did you know?

423
00:31:53,710 --> 00:31:55,290
The servants are talking

424
00:31:55,290 --> 00:31:56,450
about aunt’s boat sinking.

425
00:32:02,090 --> 00:32:02,720
Yam.

426
00:32:03,890 --> 00:32:05,320
What did you do?

427
00:32:05,320 --> 00:32:06,950
Why are you soaking wet?

428
00:32:39,940 --> 00:32:41,570
You ordered Yam to sink the boat,

429
00:32:41,570 --> 00:32:42,310
didn’t you?

430
00:32:44,530 --> 00:32:45,890
Tell us the truth.

431
00:32:45,890 --> 00:32:46,870
Don’t try to hide it!

432
00:32:47,230 --> 00:32:48,220
I didn’t do it!

433
00:32:49,260 --> 00:32:50,960
Even if Yam did,

434
00:32:50,960 --> 00:32:51,980
I don’t know anything.

435
00:32:52,750 --> 00:32:54,790
If you didn’t give the order,

436
00:32:54,790 --> 00:32:56,480
how would he dare?

437
00:32:57,350 --> 00:33:00,070
Biting the hand that feeds you!

438
00:33:00,760 --> 00:33:01,400
You

439
00:33:01,400 --> 00:33:02,510
and your master

440
00:33:03,030 --> 00:33:04,840
are wicked to the core!

441
00:33:05,350 --> 00:33:06,070
Prik!

442
00:33:09,390 --> 00:33:12,590
You wanted me dead,

443
00:33:12,590 --> 00:33:15,260
but Noi took the fall instead.

444
00:33:15,260 --> 00:33:16,750
She drowned,

445
00:33:16,750 --> 00:33:19,380
no clue if she’s dead or alive.

446
00:33:19,750 --> 00:33:20,630
Whip him!

447
00:33:21,150 --> 00:33:21,730
Yes, ma’am.

448
00:33:27,060 --> 00:33:27,970
Stop it, Prik!

449
00:33:30,640 --> 00:33:31,550
P’Hora

450
00:33:31,550 --> 00:33:32,900
Look at him.

451
00:33:33,110 --> 00:33:35,520
Dech heard it clearly,

452
00:33:35,840 --> 00:33:37,320
but he still refuses.

453
00:33:37,580 --> 00:33:39,540
Not even a shred of gratitude,

454
00:33:39,540 --> 00:33:43,110
after everything she's done for you.

455
00:33:43,110 --> 00:33:45,670
Trying to kill her like this.

456
00:33:45,670 --> 00:33:47,910
How rotten are you?!

457
00:33:56,150 --> 00:33:56,790
Yam.

458
00:33:57,610 --> 00:33:58,390
Go back!

459
00:33:58,390 --> 00:33:59,150
Gaew.

460
00:33:59,930 --> 00:34:00,870
Stop.

461
00:34:01,810 --> 00:34:02,890
I said stop!

462
00:34:03,910 --> 00:34:04,930
Look at that.

463
00:34:05,240 --> 00:34:08,760
Walking away as he pleased.

464
00:34:08,760 --> 00:34:10,480
He has no respect for us.

465
00:34:10,480 --> 00:34:11,690
P’Hora,

466
00:34:11,690 --> 00:34:15,010
you have to make him confess

467
00:34:15,010 --> 00:34:16,560
that he is the culprit.

468
00:34:17,139 --> 00:34:18,560
Calm down, Jumpa.

469
00:34:19,630 --> 00:34:21,340
We don’t have proof

470
00:34:21,340 --> 00:34:22,710
that Gaew did it.

471
00:34:23,040 --> 00:34:24,429
Proof?

472
00:34:25,190 --> 00:34:28,139
Do you have to find my dead body first

473
00:34:28,139 --> 00:34:29,719
before it counts as proof?

474
00:34:29,719 --> 00:34:32,480
He almost got me killed.

475
00:34:32,889 --> 00:34:34,090
Luckily,

476
00:34:34,090 --> 00:34:35,969
milady has accumulated great merit,

477
00:34:35,969 --> 00:34:37,330
so she survived.

478
00:34:38,670 --> 00:34:40,969
I understand you.

479
00:34:41,330 --> 00:34:42,770
But we must be careful

480
00:34:44,080 --> 00:34:47,179
not to let hatred blind us.

481
00:34:47,780 --> 00:34:49,679
I can’t wait any longer.

482
00:34:51,110 --> 00:34:51,719
Dech.

483
00:34:53,010 --> 00:34:54,719
Help me.

484
00:34:56,530 --> 00:34:59,080
Use the Krishna Kali spell on him!

485
00:34:59,330 --> 00:35:00,110
Jumpa.

486
00:35:44,730 --> 00:35:45,320
Dech.

487
00:35:45,620 --> 00:35:46,520
I…

488
00:35:46,660 --> 00:35:48,310
I don’t want to do this either.

489
00:35:50,950 --> 00:35:52,070
But seeing Mother

490
00:35:52,800 --> 00:35:54,110
almost die…

491
00:35:55,580 --> 00:35:57,770
If I sit back and do nothing,

492
00:35:58,370 --> 00:36:00,210
that would make me ungrateful.

493
00:36:01,370 --> 00:36:02,950
And we all know that

494
00:36:03,840 --> 00:36:05,820
Gaew did it without a doubt.

495
00:36:07,510 --> 00:36:08,530
But if Gaew

496
00:36:08,960 --> 00:36:10,710
didn’t do anything evil,

497
00:36:12,060 --> 00:36:13,910
then this spell can’t harm him.

498
00:36:15,060 --> 00:36:16,150
And he

499
00:36:17,090 --> 00:36:18,960
will be cleared of all suspicion.

500
00:37:20,250 --> 00:37:22,330
They’re using the Krishna Kali spell on me!

501
00:37:26,350 --> 00:37:28,010
It seems P’Muen and I

502
00:37:28,010 --> 00:37:29,810
can’t live under the same sky.

503
00:37:30,790 --> 00:37:31,530
My lord.

504
00:37:31,870 --> 00:37:34,190
Please don’t do evil.

505
00:37:36,740 --> 00:37:38,310
I’m the son of a high lord!

506
00:37:39,740 --> 00:37:42,080
How could I remain still

507
00:37:42,080 --> 00:37:43,720
when they show me such contempt?

508
00:38:00,310 --> 00:38:01,040
Yam.

509
00:38:01,430 --> 00:38:02,520
I can’t breathe.

510
00:38:02,520 --> 00:38:03,440
Help me.

511
00:38:11,850 --> 00:38:13,440
Take this medicine, sir.

512
00:38:13,840 --> 00:38:14,410
Medicine.

513
00:38:27,820 --> 00:38:29,350
My lord.

514
00:38:33,370 --> 00:38:35,750
-My lord!
-I can’t breathe!

515
00:38:36,140 --> 00:38:36,920
Yam.

516
00:38:37,240 --> 00:38:38,340
I don’t want to die!

517
00:38:43,190 --> 00:38:44,120
Yes, Grandma.

518
00:38:44,970 --> 00:38:45,990
I’m on my way home.

519
00:38:46,370 --> 00:38:47,150
Alright, Great.

520
00:38:47,150 --> 00:38:48,530
Drive safely.

521
00:38:49,120 --> 00:38:50,480
I will.

522
00:38:50,480 --> 00:38:51,310
See you soon.

523
00:39:45,730 --> 00:39:47,060
I don’t want to die.

524
00:39:49,070 --> 00:39:51,850
I don’t want to die.

525
00:39:55,050 --> 00:39:56,430
I don’t want to die.

526
00:39:58,910 --> 00:39:59,670
Yam.

527
00:40:11,710 --> 00:40:13,010
I don’t want to die!

528
00:40:13,450 --> 00:40:16,450
I don’t want to die!

529
00:40:18,080 --> 00:40:18,840
My lord!

530
00:40:26,050 --> 00:40:26,930
My lord.

531
00:40:32,590 --> 00:40:33,440
My lord!

532
00:40:35,160 --> 00:40:35,990
My lord.

533
00:41:03,030 --> 00:41:03,920
My lord!

534
00:41:04,630 --> 00:41:06,660
My lord! My lord!

535
00:41:23,310 --> 00:41:23,950
Ah!

536
00:41:46,240 --> 00:41:47,220
Help!

537
00:41:47,220 --> 00:41:48,830
Please save Lord Gaew!

538
00:41:49,390 --> 00:41:50,390
What’s wrong, Yam?

539
00:41:50,390 --> 00:41:52,550
Please save Lord Gaew.

540
00:41:52,550 --> 00:41:54,360
He’s not breathing anymore.

541
00:41:58,070 --> 00:41:58,960
See?

542
00:42:00,960 --> 00:42:02,360
Do you believe me now?

543
00:42:04,510 --> 00:42:06,210
I was right.

544
00:42:06,210 --> 00:42:08,040
Gaew is the culprit.

545
00:42:12,340 --> 00:42:13,440
I’ll go see him.

546
00:42:51,490 --> 00:42:52,400
Gaew.

547
00:43:11,550 --> 00:43:13,550
No matter how much we hate each other,

548
00:43:14,870 --> 00:43:17,070
I never wanted you to die.

549
00:43:55,910 --> 00:43:56,780
Gaew.

550
00:44:39,670 --> 00:44:40,470
What?

551
00:45:03,170 --> 00:45:04,510
Just now, I…

552
00:45:07,370 --> 00:45:08,320
I’m on my way home.

553
00:45:08,770 --> 00:45:09,550
Alright, Great.

554
00:45:09,550 --> 00:45:10,890
Drive safely.

555
00:45:11,500 --> 00:45:12,870
I will.

556
00:45:12,870 --> 00:45:13,750
See you soon.

557
00:45:17,880 --> 00:45:19,030
What’s going on?

558
00:45:21,340 --> 00:45:22,570
A Thai traditional house.

559
00:45:26,520 --> 00:45:27,760
The scent of incense.

560
00:45:30,040 --> 00:45:31,360
A man wearing Chong Kraben.

561
00:45:37,690 --> 00:45:38,610
What’s happening?

562
00:45:40,120 --> 00:45:40,770
Great.

563
00:45:41,830 --> 00:45:42,760
Get a grip.

564
00:45:43,510 --> 00:45:44,360
Calm down.

565
00:45:45,040 --> 00:45:45,820
Get a grip.

566
00:45:48,350 --> 00:45:50,350
If I think logically,

567
00:45:51,490 --> 00:45:53,510
this could be a hallucination

568
00:45:53,510 --> 00:45:55,290
caused by post-traumatic stress.

569
00:45:58,310 --> 00:46:00,180
Or am I in a coma?

570
00:46:11,340 --> 00:46:12,110
That’s right!

571
00:46:13,490 --> 00:46:14,510
The lightning strike!

572
00:46:16,830 --> 00:46:17,950
My brain might lack oxygen.

573
00:46:19,610 --> 00:46:20,300
Or…

574
00:46:21,080 --> 00:46:22,820
is this an immersive hallucination?

575
00:46:25,080 --> 00:46:26,440
Gaew, calm down.

576
00:46:27,280 --> 00:46:28,270
Pull yourself together.

577
00:46:30,940 --> 00:46:32,300
