578
00:46:56,250 --> 00:46:57,510
The muscles are firm.

579
00:47:01,870 --> 00:47:03,390
The body temperature is normal.

580
00:47:10,480 --> 00:47:11,770
And the pulse is still beating.

581
00:47:13,450 --> 00:47:14,790
If this isn’t a hallucination,

582
00:47:15,510 --> 00:47:16,680
then is this person real?

583
00:47:19,140 --> 00:47:20,480
You’re talking nonsense

584
00:47:20,950 --> 00:47:22,180
like a lunatic.

585
00:48:09,450 --> 00:48:10,200
My lord!

586
00:48:22,380 --> 00:48:23,490
What the hell is going on?

587
00:48:45,200 --> 00:48:45,970
Prik.

588
00:48:46,330 --> 00:48:47,970
Didn’t he stop breathing?

589
00:48:49,030 --> 00:48:50,450
Is he a ghost?

590
00:48:56,660 --> 00:48:57,890
You’re alright.

591
00:49:03,410 --> 00:49:04,150
Great.

592
00:49:04,500 --> 00:49:05,950
Why is your dream so vivid?

593
00:49:06,370 --> 00:49:07,290
Wake up already.

